The population of Anegam was 35 in the 1960 census.<ref>{{Cite encyclopedia |year=1960 |title=Arizona |encyclopedia=World Book Encyclopedia |publisher=Field Enterprises Educational Corporation |location=Chicago |volume=A |page=557}}</ref>

Anegam appeared on the [[2010 United States census|2010 U.S. census]] as a census-designated place (CDP), with 151 residents. As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]] the population was 149.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Explore Census Data |url=https://data.census.gov/profile/Anegam_CDP,_Arizona?g=160XX00US0402270 |access-date=2024-07-03 |website=data.census.gov}}</ref>

